msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>License Spring 設定</h3> <ol> <li>在 <a href=\"https://licensespring.com\" target=\"_blank\">licensespring.com</a> 註冊 License Spring</li> <li>登入您的 License Spring 仪表板</li> <li>創建一個新產品</li> <li>從以下位置獲取您的管理 API 金鑰：帳號設定 → API 金鑰</li> <li>從以下位置獲取您的共享金鑰：產品 → 您的產品 → SDK</li> <li>記下您的產品代碼</li> </ol> <p>您需要： <strong>管理 API 金鑰</strong>、<strong>共享金鑰</strong> 和 <strong>產品代碼</strong></p>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Cryptlex Setup</h3>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Sign up for Cryptlex at <a href=\"https://cryptlex.com\" target=\"_blank\">cryptlex.com</a></li>\n"
"                    <li>Log in to your Cryptlex dashboard</li>\n"
"                    <li>Create a new product</li>\n"
"                    <li>Generate a Personal Access Token: Profile → Access Tokens → Create Token</li>\n"
"                    <li>Note your Account ID and Product ID</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>Access Token</strong>, <strong>Product ID</strong>, and <strong>Account ID</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Cryptlex 設定</h3> <ol> <li>在 <a href=\"https://cryptlex.com\" target=\"_blank\">cryptlex.com</a> 註冊 Cryptlex</li> <li>登入您的 Cryptlex 仪表板</li> <li>創建一個新產品</li> <li>生成個人訪問令牌：個人資料 → 訪問令牌 → 創建令牌</li> <li>記下您的帳號 ID 和產品 ID</li> </ol> <p>您需要： <strong>訪問令牌</strong>、<strong>產品 ID</strong> 和 <strong>帳號 ID</strong></p>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Custom API Setup</h3>\n"
"                <p>This option allows you to integrate with your own license server.</p>\n"
"                <div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n"
"                    <strong>Requirements:</strong> Your license server must implement the required REST API endpoints.\n"
"                    <a href=\"/docs/custom-license-api/\" target=\"_blank\">View API specification</a>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Ensure your license server is accessible via HTTPS</li>\n"
"                    <li>Prepare your API base URL (e.g., https://licenses.yoursite.com/api)</li>\n"
"                    <li>Prepare your authentication credentials</li>\n"
"                    <li>Map your API endpoints to Spwig operations</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>API Base URL</strong> and <strong>Authentication Credentials</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>自定義 API 設定</h3> <p>此選項允許您與自己的許可伺服器進行整合。</p> <div class=\"alert alert-warning\"> <strong>需求：</strong>您的許可伺服器必須實現所需的 REST API 端點。 <a href=\"/docs/custom-license-api/\" target=\"_blank\">查看 API 規範</a> </div> <ol> <li>確保您的許可伺服器可通过 HTTPS 訪問</li> <li>準備您的 API 基本 URL（例如：https://licenses.yoursite.com/api）</li> <li>準備您的驗證憑證</li> <li>將您的 API 端點映射到 Spwig 操作</li> </ol> <p>您需要： <strong>API 基本 URL</strong> 和 <strong>驗證憑證</strong></p>\n"
"            "

